      "last_edited_time": "2025-06-09T06:48:00.000Z",

{"to":["contact@marketminds.com"],"cc":["alex.johnson@marketminds.com"],"subject":"Customer Engagement Data Delivery – Union Trust Bank","body":"Hello Alex,

As requested, please find attached the customer-level engagement dataset for your current analysis. The file includes:
• Transaction frequency counts (per hashed customer ID)
• Product-usage segment classifications
• Most recent Net Promoter Scores

All direct identifiers have been removed in accordance with Union Trust Bank’s data-sharing policy; only hashed customer IDs remain.

Let me know if you need any additional context or formatting tweaks.

Best regards,
Jane
Customer Service Representative
Union Trust Bank"}

formatted_items.content: I’ve emailed the hashed customer-level dataset (transaction frequency, product-usage segments, and recent NPS scores) to MarketMinds and copied you for reference. Let me know if there’s anything else you need!
